      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It is a profound tragedy when the world feels so cold and indifferent, leaving you with nothing but shadows and silence.\nPlease consider that your pain is valid, but there are still people who care deeply and want to help you find light again.\nYou are not alone in this darkness, and reaching out to a trusted friend or counselor could be the first step toward healing.\nYour story is worth telling, and there is a path forward that you have the strength to take.",
